OpenSauna
=========

OpenSauna is an independent, open-source, unofficial client for the HOTWORX
member service. It is NOT affiliated with, authorized, sponsored, or endorsed
by HOTWORX, Planet Beach Franchising Corp., or any related entity.

"HOTWORX" and any related names or logos are trademarks of their respective
owners. They are used here only nominatively — to describe what this software
interoperates with — not as a claim of affiliation or endorsement.

How it works
------------
OpenSauna communicates with the same member API that the official HOTWORX
application uses, on your behalf, using credentials you supply. It implements
the network protocol independently; it contains no HOTWORX source code or
copyrighted assets.

