Security commentary
-------------------
This project documents observable shortcomings in the official application as
factual, good-faith commentary and as motivation for a better implementation.
It does not include exploits and is not intended to facilitate unauthorized
access to anyone else's account. If you are HOTWORX and would like to discuss
any of it — or fix it — pull requests and issues are welcome.
